<p><span class="anchor" id="p14"></span>وافق فى معى <span class="c2">(ع)</span> لا <span class="c2">(ك)</span> فؤ وما ... لى <span class="c2">(ل)</span> ذ <span class="c2">(م)</span> ن الخلف لعلّى <span class="c2">(ك)</span> رّما<a href="#p14" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
